verbose_text: Chusattayanond et al. [XREF_BIBR] have shown that host cell apoptosis induced by Acanthamoeba is caspase dependent, mediated by over-expression of pro apoptotic proteins in the mitochondrial pathway, while Tripathi et al. [XREF_BIBR] demonstrated the role of the cytosolic phospholipase A2alpha (cPLA2alpha) pathway in host cell apoptosis.
